parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or shift erratically, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission shifts erratically
the vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting
difficulty shifting into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wave plate can cause the transmission to slip or hesitate, leading to loss of power and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or loses power
difficulty shifting into gear
the transmission shifts erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Stabilitrak and traction control systems can cause the vehicle to lose stability and control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The Stabilitrak and traction control lights come on
the vehicle sways or loses control
difficulty steering
the vehicle stalls or loses power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
the airbag system fails to deploy
difficulty with the seatbelt system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock up, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels stiff or hard to turn
the steering wheel locks up
the power steering pump fails
the rack and pinion fails
and the vehicle is difficult to maneuver at low speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Stabilitrak system can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The Stabilitrak system warning light comes on
the vehicle loses traction
the vehicle is difficult to control
and the power steering system fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or strand the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the dashboard lights and warning lights come on
and the vehicle is difficult to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on
the airbags deploy unexpectedly
and the airbags do not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality to occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the passenger airbag is disabled
the airbag sensor is faulty
the airbag system toggles on and off
the airbag light comes on intermittently
the airbag system does not detect the presence of an occupant in the passenger seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected falling of the liftgate/tailgate can cause injury to occupants or bystanders.
symptoms: The liftgate/tailgate falls unexpectedly
the liftgate/tailgate does not stay in place
the liftgate/tailgate has a faulty sensor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine issues can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine has a slow takeoff
the engine shakes when accelerating
the fuel runs out extremely fast without notice
the speedometer barely works
the vehicle hesitates and takes time to switch gears.
